item.title: My run.bat is getting this error.. please help me!
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

IPv4 provides approximately 4.294 billion addresses.
So I’m sure no one “stole your ip”
You have something already running on port 43594, or port 5555.
Make sure you don’t already have a run.bat running from another server.
